OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FInstead officials told him he would
OL,7,Fhave to pay #7,000 to start the ten
OL,8,Fyear process of settlement.
OL,10,FHe came to the UK in 1977 from Ghana
OL,11,Fas a student, and went on to run a
OL,12,Fpopular newsagents in Wallasey as well
OL,13,Fas performing jury service and even
OL,14,Fgetting a police bravery award when he
OL,15,Fstepped in to stop a robbery.
OL,17,FHis story was covered by ITV Granada
OL,18,FReports correspondent Tim Scott in May.
