OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FSpeaking after the decision to allow
OL,7,FNelson to remain he said: "All along I
OL,8,Fhad tried to bottle every feeling in
OL,9,Fme so that my children wouldn't be
OL,10,Fworrying about me.
OL,12,F"I was so relieved that in the end, we
OL,13,Fhave won the battle.
OL,15,F"Now we hope to win the war: for the
OL,16,Fauthorities to agree that the 10-year
OL,17,Froute is inhuman, and abolish it or
OL,18,Fshorten it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
