OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHe went on to thank all those who'd
OL,7,Fsupported him and his sons Jacob and
OL,8,FAaron who were born in the UK after
OL,9,FNelson married their British mother.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank everybody who
OL,12,Fbelieved in us and supported us in
OL,13,Fwords and donations.
OL,15,F"That makes me really really happy.
OL,16,FWhen you hear birds chirping in trees
OL,17,For flying overheard, believe me - that
OL,18,Fis me and children thanking you from
OL,19,Fthe bottom of our hearts."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
