OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHis sons have also issued a statement
OL,7,Fsaying: "Dad's victory means the
OL,8,Fabsolute world to us. We are so
OL,9,Fgrateful to our legal team at the
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Immigration Aid
OL,11,FUnit and to everyone who supported us
OL,12,Fthroughout this process - from sharing
OL,13,Four story to donating, we cannot thank
OL,14,Fyou enough".
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Immigration Aid
OL,17,FUnit had helped Nelson and his family
OL,18,Fwith their legal challenge.
