OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,FHis solicitor Nicola Burgess said: "It
OL,7,Fhas been one of the privileges of my
OL,8,Fcareer to work with Nelson and his
OL,9,Fsons.
OL,11,F"I am thrilled that he will now be
OL,12,Fgranted ILR so that he has security
OL,13,Fand certainty in his retirement.
OL,15,F"It wasn't an easy process to get
OL,16,Fhere: incorrect applications, a lack
OL,17,Fof legal advice, wrong information
OL,18,Ffrom the Home Office and 2 previous
OL,19,Frefusals to grant ILR.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
