OL,3,CVictory for 'local legend' Nelson in
OL,4,Cimmigration battle to remain
OL,6,F"Despite this and despite the
OL,7,Fconsiderable financial risk to Nelson
OL,8,Fand his family he made the decision to
OL,9,Ffight on and speak out about the
OL,10,Finjustice he has experienced.
OL,12,F"Nelson's bravery in the face of a
OL,13,Fdysfunctional immigration system has
OL,14,Fbeen inspirational."
OL,16,FThe Home Office has accepted that
OL,17,FNelson's case is 'exceptional' and
OL,18,Fhave granted him leave to stay here
OL,19,F'outside the rules' and with no need
OL,20,Fto pay a fee.
